-- Etrion Completes $76 Million Project Financing for Italian Solar Plants
-- B y   T o d d   W h i t e
-- 2010-12-06T07:47:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-06/etrion-completes-76-million-project-financing-for-italian-solar-plants.html
Etrion Corp. a Swiss renewable-energy
developer, has completed a 57 million-euro ($76 million) project
financing to build four solar-power plants in Italy with a total
capacity of 15 megawatts.  Natixis, WestLB AG and Mediocreval provided the non-
recourse senior loan facility with an 18-year term, Geneva-based
Etrion said today in a filing.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Todd White at 
 twhite2@bloomberg.net  